                            <comment id="187954" author="adilger" created="Sat, 11 Mar 2017 10:18:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was fixed in the Lustre code in 2.9+ - the setstripe will inherit the parameters that are not specified from the directory.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
